    <h2>About Olav Murillo</h2>
 

  <p>Olav Alfarabi Murillo Soto was born in Mexico in 1973. He has always had a restlessness in him - a desire to express his ideas. He started off writing, and found that that relieved some anxieties he felt toward "shouting" and expressing his thoughts. Two years ago he got a digital camera, and began to express his ideas in a more visual manner. Because Olav is self-taught, he struggled in the beginning, but found things got easier when he simply started experimenting and playing with images. </p>

